[I] Information retrieval library

[T] Xapian is a Probabilistic Information Retrieval library. It is
[T] written in C++ with bindings to Perl, Python, PHP, Java, Tcl, and
[T] C#. It is an adaptable toolkit that allows developers to add advanced
[T] indexing and search facilities to their own applications.

[U] https://www.xapian.org/

[A] Olly Betts <olly@survex.com>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

